y, Cantor holds onto Tether=E2=80=99s Treasuries for it, and Tether =0Aboss=
 Giancarlo Devasini =E2=80=9Csaid privately earlier this year that Lutnick =
will use =0Ahis political clout to try to defuse threats facing Tether,=E2=
=80=9D but also:=0A=0ACantor=E2=80=99s relationship with Tether deepened wh=
en the trading firm struck a deal =0Ato invest in the crypto giant, Lutnick=
 and Devasini have each told business =0Aassociates. Under the agreement, w=
hich was made in the past year, Cantor stood =0Ato receive about a 5% owner=
ship interest in Tether. The interest, which hasn=E2=80=99t =0Abeen previou=
sly reported, was valued by Cantor at as much as $600 million, =0Aaccording=
 to some of the business associates.=0A=0AI suppose that language is ambigu=
ous, but I think it says that Cantor=E2=80=99s deal =0Awith Tether values i=
